  "title": "All-Party Parliamentary Group for Closing the Guantanamo Bay Detention Facility",
  "purpose": "To urge the UK government to: call on the US government to finally close Guantanamo; work internationally on the urgent and humane resettlement of detainees approved for release; and call on the US government to ensure that the detainees receive adequate care for their longstanding physical and mental health needs.",
